Description: Visual Pinball frontend for Linux with multi-monitor support
 PinballUX is a Visual Pinball frontend for Linux inspired by PinballX.
 It provides multi-monitor support for Playfield, Backglass, DMD, FullDMD,
 and Topper displays.
 .
 Features include:
  - Multi-monitor display management
  - VPX table launching and management
  - Media integration (videos, images, audio)
  - Keyboard and joystick/gamepad support
  - Table database with metadata
  - FTP media downloads from gameex.com
  - Automated VPinball installation
